{"tid":1306583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當局至今收超過35萬份新選民登記創04年後新高","createTime":"2019-07-11T08:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T11:51:51.000Z","uid":266724,"like":385,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"1caf93c2820ab7b902e811a3c0f1df7c97f88d9c","tid":1306583,"uid":266724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:04:42.000Z","msg":"//新一個選民登記周期本月2日結束後，選舉事務處至今收到超過35萬份地方選區選民新登記申請，數字是04年以來的新高，當年新登記選民人數是30萬3千8百多人，選舉事務處仍在點算及核實今年新登記選民數字，預料實際數字會更高，至於新選民年齡層分布，要待選民登記册才公布。<br />\n<br />\n近期政府提出逃犯條例修訂事件，不同團體鼓勵市民登記做選民，以便在今年十一月舉行的區議會選舉及來年立法會地區直選中投票。//<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1131822&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1131822%26csid%3D261_341&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8528bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=818cb376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1131822&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d2febfb9140a44cf66ca0446f15e3d7a0d997fe4","tid":1306583,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e2f573a938f74386b1d02d70ae2c465f35afe0","tid":1306583,"uid":55130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3135ab90b0eb48a0f88eff396a4a91809e7944f","tid":1306583,"uid":73340,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:05:19.000Z","msg":"要識配票"},{"pid":"8bb82fe639173229af96ecacc6e8f60918fc0265","tid":1306583,"uid":46459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"05b0899f58044077cc338cdbc93b7006710f48de","